description: Ask Alexa for a bucket list item and it will be up to get it done. Over 800 ideas on how you can get you bucket empty (or full).
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask bucket list to give me a good idea
Alexa tell bucket list to suggest an item for today
Alexa ask bucket list to get one done
name: Bucket List
shortDescription: Bucket list will suggest a bucket list item for you today.
